title: #92Noon Nordo in for PA!  Falness/Birk
description: Kevin Falness joins the show in-studio to talk about the Wild's recent turn around. Matt Birk's regular weekly appearance on the show includes an in-depth conversation about the Vikings playoff scenarios. On top of all that, there's plenty more Vikings chatter, some Gophers football news, & even some Twins talk!
